text: Faustin Mparabanyi (born 1970) is a Rwandan former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Rwandan male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Rwanda Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
